</node>
<node id="&quot;SUMMERHAYES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Summerhayes co-authored a paper with Elton in 1923, publishing the first schematic of food chains and webs."&lt;SEP&gt;"Summerhayes co-published a paper with Charles Elton in 1923, contributing to the first food web schematic."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0c9f93f77f118c5c6b3d89cffbdd6bcc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1bcf9db76c14967fea58e57752fcd527</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 18}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 87}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;NATURALISTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Naturalists are a group of scientists who previously studied communities as a single entity or a collection of species."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0c9f93f77f118c5c6b3d89cffbdd6bcc</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 18}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 87}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COMMUNITY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Community refers to a group of interacting organisms and their environment, as studied by Elton."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0c9f93f77f118c5c6b3d89cffbdd6bcc</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 18}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 87}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SPECIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Species are individual organisms within a community, as studied by Elton."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0c9f93f77f118c5c6b3d89cffbdd6bcc</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 18}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 87}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ECONOMY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Economy refers to the current economic conditions that make it highly unlikely to recover the initial investment through honey production."&lt;SEP&gt;"Economy refers to the system of production, distribution, and consumption of goods and services, as applied to the Arctic islands by Elton."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-495e02b1ab0499af1104889b54b028c2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c9f93f77f118c5c6b3d89cffbdd6bcc</data>
