<node id="&quot;SPITSBERGEN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Spitsbergen is a location where Charles Elton led an expedition in 1923, marking a significant step in his academic career."&lt;SEP&gt;"Spitsbergen is an island in the Arctic Ocean, known for its little-explored sister island, North East Land (Nordaustlandet)."</data>
