  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"World War II is a historical event during which George Binney organized operations to run through the German blockade of Sweden."&lt;SEP&gt;"World War II is a historical event that influenced the themes of the musicals during the period."&lt;SEP&gt;"World War II is an event that loomed over the 1940s, influencing the type of entertainment audiences sought."&lt;SEP&gt;"World War II was a significant conflict during which various operations were organized and medical advancements were made."</data>
