<node id="&quot;BEES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bees are essential for the operation of a hive and require an initial investment to start beekeeping."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees are social insects known for their complex communication methods and roles within the hive."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees are social insects known for their defensive behavior, honey production, and survival strategies."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees are the workers of the hive, mentioned as 'bees everywhere' and 'watch the bees coming and going'"&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees refer to a group of insects that form a colony and are managed by beekeepers for honey production and pollination."</data>
