  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Pheromones are chemical substances given off by organisms to stimulate behavioral responses in other organisms of the same species."&lt;SEP&gt;"Pheromones are chemical substances released by bees that convey specific information to other bees."</data>
