<node id="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Subsidiaries are affiliated companies under the same corporate umbrella as the Company, sharing similar responsibilities and risks."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are affiliated organizations under the Company's control, also responsible for contributions or other amounts payable with respect to the Debtor Plan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are affiliated organizations under the Company, sharing similar obligations and liabilities regarding retirement and welfare plans."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are affiliated organizations under the control of the Company, involved in similar activities such as tax filings and elections."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary companies owned by the Company, which also need to provide access and information as per the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary organizations of the Company that must comply with the agreement and take necessary actions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary organizations of the Company."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-901cbdf0bd26b111f81dd33ee6c60d30&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-043bdd01778d3f59af7fb1427df2e10b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d43b1a9be015da589b0b6eda739a9740&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54a36509f708a00c7f0056959eeeac48&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58ed7bc84d141ce850aa3bc185a549a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c1071a343df40d56b733dc82d134dca</data>
