  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"GAAP stands for Generally Accepted Accounting Principles, which dictate accounting practices and standards."&lt;SEP&gt;"GAAP stands for Generally Accepted Accounting Principles, which the Debtors must follow for paying or accruing."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d43b1a9be015da589b0b6eda739a9740&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58ed7bc84d141ce850aa3bc185a549a1</data>
