</node>
<node id="&quot;TRANSACTIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Transactions refer to specific actions or agreements that are part of the broader business operations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transactions refer to the business operations or agreements that need to be consummated."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transactions refer to the overall business activities or agreements being executed and delivered."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transactions refer to the overall business activities or agreements, particularly those involving the Supporting Lenders and the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transactions refer to the specific business activities or agreements that the Company and Supporting Lenders are working to complete."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-654abe61169209283ea2ce547101971c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c805535d666dec0363dab97d40caa228&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58ed7bc84d141ce850aa3bc185a549a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c1071a343df40d56b733dc82d134dca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65eaf63b7a750dd0565f442fc7ade844</data>
