</node>
<node id="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Supporting Lenders are a group of parties whose consent is required for mutual termination of the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are entities that are cooperating with the Company to consummate the Transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities obligated to support the transactions under certain conditions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities that support the Company in certain transactions or agreements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities that support the transaction, requiring access and information from the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or individuals who provide funding or support for a particular project or initiative."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions providing support for EndoLix, Inc.'s reorganization."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions providing support to the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions providing support to the Company.")&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions that have entered into agreements with the Company and its affiliates."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the parties providing financial support, making representations and warranties regarding their qualifications and compliance with various legal and regulatory requirements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the parties to whom the Company must deliver a certificate."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the parties to whom the Company must deliver a certificate.")</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-654abe61169209283ea2ce547101971c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9761cab8f6b28df6081e9fb1a2da2a8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24e4dd911480ec7b0b48bea1ecbf36a8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f3c125a72e39c4200edd661367d9ef3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ad6538dc8ba49e4be8ea60807b6b2d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54a36509f708a00c7f0056959eeeac48&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a8c54b5dcade8b772c67c1ccfd6db8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58ed7bc84d141ce850aa3bc185a549a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c1071a343df40d56b733dc82d134dca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-798070fb4714049d83dcfa2fc51844a1</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 1}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 34}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 115}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LAW&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Law refers to legal requirements and obligations that must be followed for the Transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Law refers to legal statutes or regulations applicable to the Supporting Lender or its properties, rights, or assets."&lt;SEP&gt;"Law refers to the applicable laws governing the access and information requirements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Law refers to the legal framework governing the actions of the Company and its subsidiaries, particularly in relation to tax matters."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-65eaf63b7a750dd0565f442fc7ade844&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54a36509f708a00c7f0056959eeeac48&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c1071a343df40d56b733dc82d134dca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58ed7bc84d141ce850aa3bc185a549a1</data>
