<node id="&quot;AFFILIATES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Affiliates are affiliated organizations of the Company that must comply with the agreement and take necessary actions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are affiliated organizations of the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related companies or entities associated with the Company, which also need to provide access and information as per the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related companies or entities that are part of the same corporate group as the Reorganized Debtors."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related companies or entities that are part of the same corporate group as the Reorganized Debtors.")&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related organizations or entities associated with the Company and Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related organizations or entities associated with the Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related organizations or entities that are associated with the Supporting Lender."</data>
