<node id="&quot;TRADE SECRETS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Trade Secrets are confidential business information that the Company is not required to disclose due to legal or confidentiality obligations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Trade Secrets refer to confidential information that the Company aims to protect from disclosure."</data>
