<node id="&quot;BUSINESS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Business refers to the operations and activities of the Company, which the Supporting Lenders may request information about."&lt;SEP&gt;"Business refers to the operations and activities of the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Business refers to the overall operations and activities of the Supporting Lender as a whole."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9761cab8f6b28df6081e9fb1a2da2a8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54a36509f708a00c7f0056959eeeac48&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c805535d666dec0363dab97d40caa228</data>
