<node id="&quot;GOVERNMENTAL ENTITY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Governmental Entities are regulatory bodies that may issue claims or initiate proceedings related to the Debtor Plan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Governmental Entity refers to any governmental agency or regulatory body that may require consents or approvals."&lt;SEP&gt;"Governmental Entity refers to any governmental body or regulatory authority that may require consents, clearances, or approvals for the Transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Governmental Entity refers to any governmental body that could initiate or be involved in proceedings against the Debtors or their plans."</data>
