  <data key="d1">"A package of bees is recommended as a starting point for beginners, offering a manageable way to begin beekeeping."&lt;SEP&gt;"Package of Bees refers to a method of starting a new bee colony, consisting of a number of worker bees and a queen bee, often used by beginners."</data>
