  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A nucleus hive, or nuc, is another recommended starting method for beginners, providing a manageable colony."&lt;SEP&gt;"Nucleus Hive (nuc) is another method of starting a new bee colony, containing a smaller established colony, often used by beginners to ease the process."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-699a06af32464879930f06ecbb0af590&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ffbea998c9de2ed6b7c59b8ae8da3878</data>
