<node id="&quot;ESTABLISHED COLONY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"An established colony is not recommended for beginners due to initial awe and apprehension, suggesting a more controlled start with packages or nucs."&lt;SEP&gt;"Established Colony is a fully developed bee colony with a queen and sufficient worker bees, often used as a reference point for comparison."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-699a06af32464879930f06ecbb0af590&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ffbea998c9de2ed6b7c59b8ae8da3878</data>
