<node id="&quot;BEEKEEPING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Beekeeping is the practice of keeping bees, including setting up a hive, managing bees, and producing honey."&lt;SEP&gt;"Beekeeping is the practice of managing beehives for the production of honey and other products, involving various tasks and challenges."&lt;SEP&gt;"Beekeeping is the practice of managing honeybee colonies, including tasks such as installing packages or nuclei hives, recognizing problems, and ensuring colony health."&lt;SEP&gt;"Beekeeping refers to the practice of raising honeybees, emphasizing the standard and manageable approach."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-495e02b1ab0499af1104889b54b028c2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-699a06af32464879930f06ecbb0af590&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24ac740bd8207b788e25e1b76a32f657&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ffbea998c9de2ed6b7c59b8ae8da3878</data>
