<node id="&quot;BELT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Belt is a powerful, resonant vocal sound within the Vocal Arc, commonly used in musical theater singing."&lt;SEP&gt;"Belt is a vocal technique used for powerful, resonant singing, often associated with musical theater and pop music."&lt;SEP&gt;"Belt is a vocal technique where the vocal cords produce sound in the lower to mid-range, often used in music theater for powerful delivery."</data>
