  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"ERISA Affiliate refers to any entity that is considered an affiliate under ERISA, sharing similar responsibilities and risks."&lt;SEP&gt;"ERISA Affiliate refers to organizations affiliated with the Company under the Employee Retirement Income Security Act (ERISA), which also share similar obligations and liabilities regarding retirement and welfare plans."</data>
