<node id="&quot;MULTIEMPLOYER PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A multiemployer plan is defined as a plan that is subject to Section 302 or Title IV of ERISA or Section 412 of the Code, and is maintained, established, sponsored, or participated in by multiple employers."&lt;SEP&gt;"Multiemployer Plan refers to a plan maintained, established, sponsored, or participated in by multiple employers, which the Company and its Subsidiaries have never maintained, established, sponsored, participated in, contributed to, or been obligated to contribute to."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-901cbdf0bd26b111f81dd33ee6c60d30</data>
