<node id="&quot;DEBTOR PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Debtor Plan is a plan provided by the Company or Subsidiary that offers benefits such as retiree or post-employment disability, life insurance, or other welfare benefits to any Person."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtor Plan refers to a specific type of plan that provides retiree or post-employment benefits, which is not provided by the Company or its Subsidiaries except as required by applicable law."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtor Plan refers to a specific type of plan that provides retiree or post-employment benefits, which the Company and its Subsidiaries do not provide except as required by applicable law."</data>
