<node id="&quot;LIFE INSURANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Life Insurance refers to insurance policies providing financial protection in case of death, but the Company and its Subsidiaries do not provide such benefits."</data>
