  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Message from the Heavens is the communication or signal received by the team from an unknown source."&lt;SEP&gt;"Message from the Heavens refers to the communication or signal received by the Company and its Subsidiaries that could rewrite human history."</data>
