  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Scale is a series of musical notes played in ascending or descending order, used in the given context to illustrate the effect of formants on voice production."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scale refers to a series of musical notes in ascending or descending order, often used to understand the relationship between different pitches."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9df53a9e4f0e74a05d58e93589ff4804&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8e95cffe887226367f1fc5b800af6dc</data>
