  <data key="d0">"ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Ascend involves moving through different pitches, which can align with formants."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9df53a9e4f0e74a05d58e93589ff4804</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 44}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUSTAIN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Sustain means holding a note or sound for a period of time, allowing for the demonstration of formant effects."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9df53a9e4f0e74a05d58e93589ff4804</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 46}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUSTAINING&quot;">
