  <data key="d6">chunk-0e8ce67d2107bdd08b0bb31d5ed05831</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;ARTICLE V&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Article V contains various representations and warranties made by the Company."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-0e8ce67d2107bdd08b0bb31d5ed05831</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;COVENANTS AND AGREEMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company makes covenants and agreements within the agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-0e8ce67d2107bdd08b0bb31d5ed05831</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;MUTUAL TERMINATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company is one of the parties involved in the mutual termination of the agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-1a8c54b5dcade8b772c67c1ccfd6db8b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;DEBTOR PLAN DOCUMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company is responsible for establishing, operating, and administering the Debtor Plan according to its terms."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-043bdd01778d3f59af7fb1427df2e10b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;ANNUAL REPORT (FORM 5500 OR 990 SERIES)&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company is responsible for preparing and submitting the annual report (Form 5500 or 990 series) to the IRS."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-043bdd01778d3f59af7fb1427df2e10b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;ACTUARIAL REPORT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company is responsible for obtaining and maintaining the most recently prepared actuarial report related to the Debtor Plan."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-043bdd01778d3f59af7fb1427df2e10b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;MATERIAL CORRESPONDENCE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company is responsible for receiving and sending material correspondence to or from any Governmental Entity related to the Debtor Plan."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-043bdd01778d3f59af7fb1427df2e10b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;SUMMARY PLAN DESCRIPTION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company is responsible for providing the most recent summary plan description and any summaries of all material modifications related to the Debtor Plan."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-043bdd01778d3f59af7fb1427df2e10b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;IRS DETERMINATION OR OPINION LETTER&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company is responsible for obtaining the most recent IRS determination or opinion letter related to the Debtor Plan."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-043bdd01778d3f59af7fb1427df2e10b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;DEBTORS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Debtors are responsible for ensuring compliance with GAAP and managing material liabilities, including those of the Company." )|&gt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d43b1a9be015da589b0b6eda739a9740</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;ERISA PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company and its Subsidiaries must ensure that ERISA Plans do not engage in transactions that could result in civil penalties or taxes." )|&gt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d43b1a9be015da589b0b6eda739a9740</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;MULTIEMPLOYER PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company has never maintained, established, sponsored, participated in, contributed to, or been obligated to contribute to, or otherwise incurred any obligation or liability under any multiemployer plan within the six-year period prior to the date of this Agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-901cbdf0bd26b111f81dd33ee6c60d30</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;DEBTOR PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">27.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company does not provide Debtor Plans that provide retiree or post-employment benefits, except as required by Applicable Law."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company does not provide retiree or post-employment medical, disability, life insurance or other welfare benefits to any Person, and has no obligation to provide such benefits."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company sponsors Debtor Plans that provide benefits to Persons."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-495e02b1ab0499af1104889b54b028c2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-901cbdf0bd26b111f81dd33ee6c60d30</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;ERISA AFFILIATE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"ERISA Affiliate is an organization affiliated with the Company under ERISA, sharing similar obligations and liabilities regarding retirement and welfare plans."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-901cbdf0bd26b111f81dd33ee6c60d30</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;APPLICABLE LAW&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company and its Subsidiaries comply with Applicable Law, but do not provide certain benefits unless required by law."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-901cbdf0bd26b111f81dd33ee6c60d30</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;RETIREE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company does not provide benefits to Retirees, except as required by Applicable Law."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-901cbdf0bd26b111f81dd33ee6c60d30</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;POST-EMPLOYMENT MEDICAL BENEFITS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company does not provide Post-Employment Medical Benefits, except as required by Applicable Law."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-901cbdf0bd26b111f81dd33ee6c60d30</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;DISABILITY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company does not provide Disability benefits, except as required by Applicable Law."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-901cbdf0bd26b111f81dd33ee6c60d30</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;LIFE INSURANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company does not provide Life Insurance, except as required by Applicable Law."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-901cbdf0bd26b111f81dd33ee6c60d30</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;WELFARE BENEFITS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company does not provide Welfare Benefits, except as required by Applicable Law."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-901cbdf0bd26b111f81dd33ee6c60d30</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SCOUT BEE&quot;" target="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Scout Bee discovers new nectar sources and informs the Bee Colony about these sources, contributing to the colony's foraging efforts."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SCOUT BEE&quot;" target="&quot;NEW SOURCE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Scout Bee discovers New Sources and signals their location and value to the Hive."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;NECTAR SOURCE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony forages from Nectar Sources, with some bees acting as scouts to find the most rewarding sources."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;EXISTING SOURCE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony forages from Existing Sources that are still producing nectar."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bee Colony forages from Existing Sources, with some bees acting as scouts to find new sources."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;BEE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee is a member of the Bee Colony that forages for nectar and communicates with the Hive."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;FLOWER&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony forages from Flowers, which are specific types of nectar sources."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;PLANT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony forages from Plants, which are general sources of nectar."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;BLOOM&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony forages during the Bloom period when plants produce flowers and nectar."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;FORAGING&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony engages in Foraging activities to gather nectar from various sources."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;SIGNAL&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony uses Signal methods to communicate the location and value of new nectar sources to the Hive."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;COLLECTING&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony engages in Collecting activities to gather nectar from nectar sources."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;PROCESSING&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony engages in Processing activities to convert nectar into honey within the Hive."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;WAGGLE DANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony uses the Waggle Dance to indicate the direction and distance of nectar sources."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;INDEFINITE PERIOD&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony remains faithful to a nectar source for an Indefinite Period."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;NEW SOURCE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony forages from New Sources discovered by Scout Bees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;RELATIVE VALUE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony compares the Relative Value of different nectar sources."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;ECONOMIC VALUE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony considers the Economic Value of nectar sources for the colony."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;COLONY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony is a group of Bees that work together to gather and process nectar."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony indirectly affects the Company's Tax situation through its foraging activities."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony's activities contribute to the Company's Tax Return preparation."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;TAX PERIOD&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony's foraging activities occur within the Tax Period."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;TAX ELECTION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony's activities may influence the Company's Tax Elections."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;TAX REFUND&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony's activities may lead to a Tax Refund for the Company."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;TAX AUDIT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony's activities may be subject to a Tax Audit by the government."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;TAX COMPLIANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Colony's activities contribute to the Company's Tax Compliance efforts."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-60a04f9021aa4469d11bdecb7939dedb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARY&quot;" target="&quot;DEBTOR PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Subsidiary also sponsors Debtor Plans that provide benefits to Persons."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-495e02b1ab0499af1104889b54b028c2</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TAX&quot;" target="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are part of the Company and thus are also involved in tax-related activities."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-58ed7bc84d141ce850aa3bc185a549a1</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;GAAP&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"GAAP applies to the accounting practices and standards that Subsidiaries must follow."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-58ed7bc84d141ce850aa3bc185a549a1</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">12.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders do not directly involve Subsidiaries in their activities but are part of the broader transactional context."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-58ed7bc84d141ce850aa3bc185a549a1</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;LAW&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries operate within the same legal framework as the Company."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-58ed7bc84d141ce850aa3bc185a549a1</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;INVENTORY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries hold inventory as part of their assets."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-58ed7bc84d141ce850aa3bc185a549a1</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;GAAP COMPLIANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries must comply with GAAP for financial reporting."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-58ed7bc84d141ce850aa3bc185a549a1</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;MATERIAL TAX LOSSES, CREDITS, AND ATTRIBUTES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may use material tax losses, credits, and attributes to reduce tax liabilities."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-58ed7bc84d141ce850aa3bc185a549a1</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;DEBTOR PLAN DOCUMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are also responsible for establishing, operating, and administering the Debtor Plan according to its terms."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-043bdd01778d3f59af7fb1427df2e10b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;ANNUAL REPORT (FORM 5500 OR 990 SERIES)&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are also responsible for contributing to the preparation and submission of the annual report (Form 5500 or 990 series) to the IRS."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-043bdd01778d3f59af7fb1427df2e10b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;ACTUARIAL REPORT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are also responsible for contributing to the maintenance of the most recently prepared actuarial report related to the Debtor Plan."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-043bdd01778d3f59af7fb1427df2e10b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;MATERIAL CORRESPONDENCE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are also responsible for contributing to the receipt and sending of material correspondence to or from any Governmental Entity related to the Debtor Plan."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-043bdd01778d3f59af7fb1427df2e10b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;SUMMARY PLAN DESCRIPTION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are also responsible for contributing to the provision of the most recent summary plan description and any summaries of all material modifications related to the Debtor Plan."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-043bdd01778d3f59af7fb1427df2e10b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;IRS DETERMINATION OR OPINION LETTER&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are also responsible for contributing to the obtaining of the most recent IRS determination or opinion letter related to the Debtor Plan."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-043bdd01778d3f59af7fb1427df2e10b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;ERISA PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are also subject to the same ERISA compliance requirements as the Company." )|&gt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d43b1a9be015da589b0b6eda739a9740</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;MULTIEMPLOYER PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries share similar obligations and liabilities regarding multiemployer plans as the Company."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-901cbdf0bd26b111f81dd33ee6c60d30</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
