  <data key="d4">35.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lender is involved in specific transactions as part of the business operations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lender is involved in the execution and delivery of agreements and instruments related to the Transactions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c805535d666dec0363dab97d40caa228&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65eaf63b7a750dd0565f442fc7ade844</data>
