  <data key="d4">32.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Access and Information is an event where the Supporting Lenders confirm their access to necessary information and cooperation with the other parties."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders receive access and information from the Company as per the agreement."</data>
