  <data key="d5">"EndoLix, Inc. is receiving support from the Supporting Lenders for its reorganization."&lt;SEP&gt;"EndoLix, Inc. is seeking support from the Supporting Lenders for its reorganization process."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Supporting Lenders are providing financial support to EndoLix, Inc. for its reorganization."</data>
