  <data key="d4">45.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Supporting Lenders are involved in the reorganization process of EndoLix, Inc."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Supporting Lenders are part of the reorganization process by agreeing to support EndoLix, Inc."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Supporting Lenders are providing financial support for the reorganization of EndoLix, Inc."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Supporting Lenders are providing necessary financial support for the reorganization of EndoLix, Inc."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Supporting Lenders are providing support for EndoLix, Inc.'s reorganization."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8f3c125a72e39c4200edd661367d9ef3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
