  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Consents and Approvals is an event where the Supporting Lenders confirm they have obtained all necessary consents and approvals to enter into the agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8ad6538dc8ba49e4be8ea60807b6b2d5</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;NO VIOLATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"No Violations is an event where the Supporting Lenders confirm they have not violated any laws, regulations, or agreements."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8ad6538dc8ba49e4be8ea60807b6b2d5</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;BROKERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Brokers are entities that may be involved in facilitating the transactions or providing services to the Supporting Lenders, indicating a potential relationship."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8ad6538dc8ba49e4be8ea60807b6b2d5</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;OWNERSHIP OF CLAIMS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Ownership of Claims is an event where the Supporting Lenders confirm their ownership of certain claims or rights."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8ad6538dc8ba49e4be8ea60807b6b2d5</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;INTERIM OPERATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
