  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Sound can be referenced to middle-C, a specific pitch often used as a tuning reference."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-e8e95cffe887226367f1fc5b800af6dc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
