</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EE&quot;" target="&quot;E4&quot;">
  <data key="d4">20.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"E4 is the pitch corresponding to the ee vowel in a C-Major triad in first inversion, open position."&lt;SEP&gt;"ee corresponds to the pitch E4 in a C-Major triad in first inversion, open position, according to the mnemonic 'every child gets candy eagerly'. "</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-e8e95cffe887226367f1fc5b800af6dc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
